oracle.adf.share.logging.internal
Class LoggingConstants

java.lang.Object
  oracle.adf.share.logging.internal.LoggingConstants

public final class LoggingConstants
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains some common constants used by the internal implementation of the logging framework. Therefore, it is declared as final(not subclassable), and its constructor is private(uninstantiable).
